claim.claim-text:
1. A hand-held gardening tool comprising: 
a pair of spatially separated structural members of a selected length terminating in first ends and second ends and having midpoints along their length; 
a head for use as an implement in gardening activities having a cultivating claw or a blade edge attached to the first ends of the structural members; 
a handle dimensioned and configured to be gripped by one hand during use in gardening activities disposed and attached between the structural members at about the midpoints of the structural members; 
an arm strap dimensioned and configured to receive the arm of a gardener during gardening activities disposed and attached between the structural members near the second ends of the structural members.
